OL,3,CPlans to cut Cardiff University
OL,4,Cnursing school paused amid alternative
OL,5,Cproposal
OL,7,FPlans to close Cardiff University's
OL,8,Fschool of nursing have been put on
OL,9,Fhold while it considers an
OL,10,F"alternative plan".
OL,12,FIn January, the university announced
OL,13,Fwidely-criticised proposals to cut 400
OL,14,Fstaff across the institution and scrap
OL,15,Fsome departments, including nursing.
