OL,3,CPlans to cut Cardiff University
OL,4,Cnursing school paused amid alternative
OL,5,Cproposal
OL,7,FAn email to staff said the new
OL,8,Fproposal would mean teaching fewer
OL,9,Fundergraduate nursing students each
OL,10,Fyear, but it would continue to offer
OL,11,Fadult, child and mental health nursing
OL,12,Fprogrammes.
OL,14,FThe overall 400 job cuts proposal
OL,15,Fcould now be scaled down to 286 across
OL,16,Fthe organisation, following the
OL,17,Facceptance of voluntary redundancy
OL,18,Fapplications.
