OL,3,CPlans to cut Cardiff University
OL,4,Cnursing school paused amid alternative
OL,5,Cproposal
OL,7,FAn email sent by Professor Stephen
OL,8,FRiley, pro vice-chancellor of the
OL,9,FCollege of Biomedical and Life
OL,10,FSciences, said: "The alternative
OL,11,Fproposal would mean teaching fewer
OL,12,Fundergraduate students each year, but
OL,13,Ffocusing heavily on the student
OL,14,Fexperience and support provided
OL,15,Fthroughout the degree. This should
OL,16,Fresult in a higher proportion of
OL,17,Fstudents successfully graduating and
OL,18,Fmoving into the Welsh NHS.
