OL,7,F"There are elements of the proposal
OL,8,Fthat are outside the university's
OL,9,Fcontrol ` for example, the proposal
OL,10,Fthat the university receives the full
OL,11,Ffee of #9,535 for nursing students,
OL,12,Frather than the #9,000 received
OL,13,Fcurrently, this is a Wales-wide issue.
OL,14,FWe also need to discuss with our
OL,15,Fstakeholders how many international
OL,16,Fnursing students we can take."
