OL,7,FVice Chancellor Professor Wendy Larner
OL,8,Fconfirmed that staff in the chemistry
OL,9,Fand maths departments are no longer at
OL,10,Frisk of redundancy.
OL,12,FThe university is on track to reduce
OL,13,Fits full-time headcount by 114 after
OL,14,F81 members of staff opted for
OL,15,Fvoluntary redundancy, alongside a
OL,16,Fnumber of voluntary severance
OL,17,Fapplications.
